<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>wḥdk nwr ạlạ̉nwạr</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạlqrạr- wḥdk nwr ạlạ̉nwạr .. wḥdk br ạlạ̉brạr
 wḥdk ṭhr ạlạ̉ṭhạr .. (yạ ạ̹lhy yswʿ ạlbạr)2
 1- wḥdk rb ạlqwạt .. wḥdk ḍy ạlsmwạt
 wlkl ạlmkẖlwqạt .. (ạ̹nt ạlḥyạẗ yạ yswʿ)2
 2- wḥdk ṣạḥb ạlslṭạn .. wạnt ạlrb ạldyạn
 ysjd lk kl kyạn .. (wyrnm lạsm yswʿ)2
 3- wḥdk ṣkẖr ạlạ̉kwạn .. wḥdk nwr ạlạ̹ymạn
 wḥdk fạdy ạlạ̹nsạn .. (wkẖlạṣ ậdm yạ yswʿ)2
 4- wḥdk fạdy ạlkẖṭạẗ .. wḥdk mʿṭy ạlḥyạẗ
 wạltrạnym wạlṣlạẗ .. (ạ̹lyk wḥdk yạ yswʿ)2
 5- (wḥdk yswʿ ạlmḥbwb .. tsjd lk kl sẖʿwb
 wtậmn byk wttwb .. ʿn kẖṭạyạhạ yạ yswʿ)2
 6- (wḥdk wlạ ḥd swạk .. kẖlṣnạ mn ạlhlạk
 lạ rỷys wlạ ạ̉y mlạk .. lạ ạ̹lh gẖyrk yạ yswʿ)2
 7- (wḥdk rạʿy ạlrʿạẗ .. wḥdk rb ạlḥyạẗ
 nsjd lk yạ ạbn ạllh .. nʿbd ạsmk yạ yswʿ)2</lyrics>
<author>mạhr fạyz, mạhr fạyz</author>
<hymn_number>1585</hymn_number>
</song>